Baltimore Ravens head coach John Harbaugh yells during the second half of an NFL football game against the San Francisco 49ers in Santa Clara, Calif., Sunday, Oct. 18, 2015. (AP Photo/Marcio Jose Sanchez) Posted: Monday, October 19, 2015 11:23 am | Updated: 1:00 pm, Mon Oct 19, 2015. It's all going wrong for some NFL slumpers Associated Press | 
There are slumps in the NFL, and there are SLUMPS. 
Sure, the Jaguars, Titans, Browns, Bears and Redskins have poor records so far. That was pretty much expected.
